data.description: Welcome to your peaceful oasis! This charming home sits on .59 acres, offering breathtaking views of the surrounding mountains from both the back patio and the living room. Located within 1/2 mile of the RedHawk championship Golf course or you can trophy bass fish at Lake Lowell right down the street. With three bedrooms, three and a half bathrooms, and a two-car garage, there's plenty of space for comfortable living. The roof was replaced just three years ago, ensuring peace of mind for years to come. The heat pump was also recently updated six years ago, along with a new well pump installation. Plus, enjoy the freedom of no HOA so trailer or RV parking no problem! The basement features a separate access door, perfect for potential separate living quarters or additional space to suit your needs.
